overview: Maid of Honor Lily (Julia Robbie) is desperate to find a plus one for her best friend's wedding. Having already planned an evening with Liv Revamped, Julia is set up on a blind date with Ryan Driller - at the same time and at the same restaurant! Confronted with a tough choice, she does what any young, hot, and sexually adventurous girl would do. She has an unforgettable date night threesome! The only question is if she can have a plus two for the wedding.
tagline: From Chronically Single to Ready to Mingle!
title: Double Booked Date Night
